  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Body mass index equal to or less than 28;

          -  Exclusive palmar hyperhidrosis or palmar hyperhidrosis associated with axillary and /
             or plantar hyperhidrosis;

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Being sinister (or left-handed);

          -  Craneo-f acial or generalized hyperhidrosis;

          -  Coagulopathies;

          -  Previous thoracic surgery;

          -  Other comorbidities such as cardiological, metabolic, infectious or neoplastic
             diseases;

          -  Pregnancy;
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
